an prevent the public from seeing your personal listening habits if you so choose.',0,'1','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; en) Opera 8.50','',0,0),(74,25,'your site','teyler4@gmail.com','http://hirschland-immobilien.info','118.123.16.120','2016-06-04 02:49:56','2016-06-03 18:49:56','Apple now has Rhapsody as an app, which is a great start, but it is currently hampered by the inability to store locally on your iPod, and has a dismal 64kbps bit rate. If this changes, then it will somewhat negate this advantage for the Zune, but the 10 songs per month will still be a big plus in Zune Pass\' favor.',0,'1','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; en) Opera 8.50','',0,0),(75,1,'Normand Frueh','Ronne@gmail.com','http://www.0vk8l9Vwbj.com/0vk8l9Vwbj','118.123.16.120','2016-06-04 04:39:45','2016-06-03 20:39:45','Oh my goodness! Amazing article dude! Many thanks, However I am experiencing troubles with your RSS. I don’t know the reason why I cannot join it. Is there anyone else getting identical RSS problems? Anyone who knows the answer can you kindly respond? Thanx!!|',0,'1','Mozilla/4.0 (compatible; MSIE 6.0; Windows NT 5.1; en) Opera 8.50','',0,0),(76,25,'webmaster','tennent@ymail.com','http://hockey-cosom.info','118.123.16.120','2016-06-04 05:19:36','2016-06-03 21:19:36','This is getting a bit more subjective, but I much prefer the Zune Marketplace. The interface is colorful, has more flair, and some cool features like \'Mixview\' that let you quickly see related albums, songs, or other users related to what you\'re listening to. Clicking on one of those will center on that item, and another set of \"neighbors\" will come into view, allowing you to navigate around exploring by similar artists, songs, or users. Speaking of users, the Zune \"Social\" is also great fun, letting you find others with shared tastes and becoming friends with them. You then can listen to a playlist created based on an amalgamation of what all your friends are listeni